their life or in their freedom.

00:09:29.940 --> 00:09:33.040
And we have honored that for generations.

00:09:33.040 --> 00:09:37.003
We have been that place that
allows refugees to come in.

00:09:38.170 --> 00:09:39.250
We've been that place

00:09:39.250 --> 00:09:41.250
that have allowed immigrants to come in.

00:09:42.270 --> 00:09:44.393
